data.description: When you enter you will go WOW!  Gated community with lawn maintenance included! TH has NEW ceiling fans, luxury vinyl floor, granite countertops, black door knobs and hinges, kitchen hardware, water heater and appliances AND freshly painted!!  Total turn-key, move-right in!  Conveniently located near the base and airport, and both 526 and 26 to easily get downtown or to the beach!  The neighborhood has a swimming pool, gated playground, clubhouse and even tennis courts!  Enjoy relaxing on your screened in porch with quiet privacy, and there is one bedroom downstairs with access to full bath, and additional two larger bedrooms upstairs that share a jack-n-jill full bath.  There is plenty of storage space under the stairs and in the ample sized closets.  VA and FHA financing should be fine
